---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Services — Surrey Contracting Limited"
  description="Our services — groundworks, bulk earthworks and commercial surfacing. Self-delivered by one experienced team across Surrey."
  path="/services"
  active="services"
>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="page-hero-img" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/groundworks.webp')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero-vignette"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="container page-hero-inner">
    <nav class="crumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/index">Home</a>
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="12" height="12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M9 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
      <span>Services</span>
    </nav>
    <h1 class="page-title">Services</h1>
    <p class="page-lede">Self-delivered demolition, groundworks, bulk earthworks and commercial surfacing across Surrey — one team, one programme, signed off to one standard.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section svc-intro">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">What we deliver</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">A full-service contractor for any site.</h2>
      <p class="section-lede">From the first survey to the final reinstatement, four core disciplines under one roof. Self-delivered, properly priced, properly programmed.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="svc-detail" id="demolition">
  <div class="container svc-detail-grid">
    <div class="svc-detail-media">
      <div class="svc-detail-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/demolition.jpg')"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-detail-copy">
      <h2 class="section-title">Demolition</h2>
      <p class="lede-dark">Commercial and residential demolition services — site clearance, internal soft strip, concrete crushing and site hoarding, all meticulously planned and executed with safety and precision.</p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>Commercial &amp; residential demolition</li>
        <li>Site clearance &amp; enabling works</li>
        <li>Internal soft strip demolition</li>
        <li>Concrete crushing &amp; recycling</li>
        <li>Site hoarding &amp; security</li>
        <li>Waste management &amp; disposal</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/demolition" class="btn btn-yellow">Learn more about demolition →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="svc-detail svc-detail-alt" id="groundworks">
  <div class="container svc-detail-grid svc-detail-reverse">
    <div class="svc-detail-media">
      <div class="svc-detail-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/groundworks.webp')"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-detail-copy">
      <h2 class="section-title">Groundworks</h2>
      <p class="lede-dark">Comprehensive groundwork solutions for commercial and residential developments — site preparation, foundations, drainage, excavation and infrastructure works.</p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>Strip foundations, trench fill &amp; piled caps</li>
        <li>Surface-water &amp; foul drainage</li>
        <li>Service ducting &amp; ICTs</li>
        <li>Substructure, oversite &amp; slab</li>
        <li>Retaining walls &amp; gabion structures</li>
        <li>Site clearance, reduce dig &amp; muck-away</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/groundworks" class="btn btn-yellow">Learn more about groundworks →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="svc-detail svc-detail-alt" id="bulk-earthworks">
  <div class="container svc-detail-grid">
    <div class="svc-detail-media">
      <div class="svc-detail-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/bulk-earthworks.jpg')"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-detail-copy">
      <h2 class="section-title">Bulk Earthworks</h2>
      <p class="lede-dark">Large-scale excavation, site levelling, land remediation and earthmoving — delivered with modern plant and machinery, expertly operated.</p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>Cut &amp; fill operations to levels &amp; tolerances</li>
        <li>Site strip, topsoil management &amp; stockpiling</li>
        <li>Bulk muck-away with own &amp; partner fleet</li>
        <li>Land remediation &amp; capping</li>
        <li>Attenuation basins, ponds &amp; bunds</li>
        <li>Plant: tracked excavators 1.5T–35T, dozers, dumpers, rollers</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/earthworks" class="btn btn-yellow">Learn more about earthworks →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="svc-detail" id="commercial-surfacing">
  <div class="container svc-detail-grid svc-detail-reverse">
    <div class="svc-detail-media">
      <div class="svc-detail-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/surfacing.jpg')"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-detail-copy">
      <h2 class="section-title">Commercial Surfacing</h2>
      <p class="lede-dark">Professional surfacing solutions for commercial premises, car parks, roads, industrial estates and access routes — using high-quality tarmac, asphalt and surfacing materials.</p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>Tarmac &amp; asphalt — base, binder &amp; surface course</li>
        <li>Car park construction &amp; resurfacing</li>
        <li>Estate roads &amp; access routes</li>
        <li>Precast &amp; in-situ kerbing</li>
        <li>Resin-bound &amp; resin-bonded surfaces</li>
        <li>Line marking &amp; signage reinstatement</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/surfacing" class="btn btn-yellow">Learn more about surfacing →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section page-section-grey">
  <div class="container svc-residential">
    <div class="svc-res-copy">
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-yellow">Plus residential</span>
      <h3>Premium driveways, paving &amp; patios.</h3>
      <p>Alongside our commercial work we deliver high-quality residential surfacing — tarmac driveways, resin-bound, block paving, pathways and external landscaping.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-res-tags">
      <span>Tarmac Driveways</span>
      <span>Resin Bound</span>
      <span>Block Paving</span>
      <span>Pathways &amp; Patios</span>
      <span>External Landscaping</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-strip">
  <div class="container cta-strip-row">
    <div>
      <h3>Got a site to discuss?</h3>
      <p>Free measured visit within 5 working days, itemised proposal soon after.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-strip-ctas">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-yellow">Request a quote</a>
      <a href="tel:01932932650" class="btn btn-ghost-light">01932 932650</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</BaseLayout>
